General requirements:
* Python >= 2.5

Additional requirements that will be downloaded automatically:
* NumPy (http://numpy.scipy.org/, apt-get install python-numpy)
* PyCrypto (http://www.dlitz.net/software/pycrypto/)

Proxy client installation requirements that you must install
manually:
* Selenium, patched to support Collage (http://www.gtnoise.net/collage)
* wxPython (http://wxpython.org)

Proxy server installation requirements that you must install manually:
* lighttpd (http://www.lighttpd.net/, apt-get install lighttpd)
* spawn-fcgi (http://redmine.lighttpd.net/projects/spawn-fcgi, apt-get install spawn-fcgi)
* cherrypy (http://www.cherrypy.org, apt-get install python-cherrypy)
* cheetah (http://www.cheetahtemplate.org, apt-get install python-cheetah)

Proxy server requirements that will be downloaded automatically:
* flickrapi Python package (http://stuvel.eu/projects/flickrapi, apt-get install python-flickrapi)
* Python Imaging Library (http://www.pythonware.com/products/pil, apt-get install python-imaging)
